.TH "axienet_ethtools_set_pauseparam" 9 "axienet_ethtools_set_pauseparam" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
axienet_ethtools_set_pauseparam \- Set device pause parameter(flow control) settings.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" axienet_ethtools_set_pauseparam
.BI "(struct net_device *ndev "  ","
.BI "struct ethtool_pauseparam *epauseparm "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ndev" 12
Pointer to net_device structure
.IP "epauseparm" 12
Pointer to ethtool_pauseparam structure
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This implements ethtool command for enabling flow control on Rx and Tx
paths. Issue "ethtool -A ethX tx on|off" under linux prompt to execute this
function.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, -EFAULT if device is running
